{"tid":2084877,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"辯方求情：想救年輕人","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:48:02.000Z","uid":2769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"95b34578cc36e5798137e7fe019dd0e18f82957e","tid":2084877,"uid":2769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"民陣去年 6 月 9 日發起反修例遊行，翌日凌晨有示威者在立法會外留守，並發生警民衝突，多人被捕，當中 5 人被控非法集結、襲警等罪，案件今（29 日） 在東區裁判法院提堂。其中一名 33 歲裝修工人承認一項參與非法集結，另一名同齡的社工承認一項參與非法集結及一項襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，裝修工人妻子因此案與其離婚，亦與父親關係變差；而社工則因見警方正在拘捕年青人時，希望救出他們，才愚蠢地襲警。二人押後至 7 月 13 日判刑，以等候背景報告及社會服務令報告，並需即時還押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/69%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8C%E6%B6%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC-%E4%B8%80%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E8%AA%8D%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85-%E6%83%B3%E6%95%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%BA/#.Xvnc5XmXSlo.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F69%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%23.Xvnc5XmXSlo.facebook&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTd%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=1f01dd99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F69%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E